longBusinessSummary: AcouSort AB (publ), a technology company, develops components and instruments used in the diagnostics, analytics, and cell therapy processing markets. It offers AcouTrap, a benchtop research instrument for sample preparation of cells, extracellular vesicles, bacteria, and viruses from various media; AcouPlasma, an module that enables in-line analysis of blood plasma from whole blood samples; AQC Module, an in-line optical analysis of particle suspensions for quality control or monitoring applications; and AcouWash, a benchtop research instrument for label-free separation of target cells from various samples. The company has collaboration agreement with global life science company to develop cell therapy. AcouSort AB and Bio-ReCell Ltd. announced that the two companies have signed a Letter of Intent to jointly develop a system for automated clean-up and isolation of stem cells and immune cells from adipose tissue. AcouSort AB (publ) was founded in 2010 and is based in Lund, Sweden.

AcouSort AB and Bio-ReCell Ltd. announced that the two companies have signed a Letter of Intent to jointly develop a system for automated clean-up and isolation of stem cells and immune cells from adipose tissue. AcouSort AB (publ) was founded in 2010 and is based in Lund, Sweden.

AcouSort AB and Bio-ReCell Ltd. announced that the two companies have signed a Letter of Intent to jointly develop a system for automated clean-up and isolation of stem cells and immune cells from adipose tissue. AcouSort AB (publ) was founded in 2010 and is based in Lund, Sweden.

AcouSort AB and Bio-ReCell Ltd. announced that the two companies have signed a Letter of Intent to jointly develop a system for automated clean-up and isolation of stem cells and immune cells from adipose tissue. AcouSort AB (publ) was founded in 2010 and is based in Lund, Sweden.

AcouSort AB and Bio-ReCell Ltd. announced that the two companies have signed a Letter of Intent to jointly develop a system for automated clean-up and isolation of stem cells and immune cells from adipose tissue. AcouSort AB (publ) was founded in 2010 and is based in Lund, Sweden.

AcouSort AB and Bio-ReCell Ltd. announced that the two companies have signed a Letter of Intent to jointly develop a system for automated clean-up and isolation of stem cells and immune cells from adipose tissue. AcouSort AB (publ) was founded in 2010 and is based in Lund, Sweden.

AcouSort AB and Bio-ReCell Ltd. announced that the two companies have signed a Letter of Intent to jointly develop a system for automated clean-up and isolation of stem cells and immune cells from adipose tissue. AcouSort AB (publ) was founded in 2010 and is based in Lund, Sweden.
